title: Duck Sauce - Quack (Unofficial Soundcloud Rip) [128kbps]
description:
Duck Sauce - Quack LP

This is, as the title states, and unofficial rip that I grabbed using a soundcloud downloader and the links from Duck Sauce's page. It's only in 128kbps so when it comes out on April 15th I'd suggest looking back on TPB and getting a new version. Regardless, if you want all the music in pretty decent quality, here you go. All tags should be set for iTunes even though their file names are awful. Have fun.
